{"tid":96253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地方媽媽上了女兒的5同學　淫蕩玩3P","createTime":"2017-01-26T16:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T01:33:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93e6da7c562871db1a4f9df3405a69d0dc7ec2fc","tid":96253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:30:44.000Z","msg":"美國佛羅里達一名40歲地方媽媽阿耶(Jaimie Ayer)，與女兒的2名同學玩3P，還被女兒撞見。警方調查後更發現，阿耶總共上了女兒的5名同學。 <br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，阿耶的女兒在去年12月23日辦了一場派對，會中有女兒的多名同學參加，阿耶則是和一群男同學尬喝酒。派對舉行到一半的時候，阿耶突然說想去洗澡，要求現場一名男同學「幫她」。然後阿耶就帶男同學去房間，開始扒他的衣服並做愛。隨後有一名男同學也「加入戰局」，這時剛好被阿耶的女兒撞見，看到媽媽正在與一名16歲和17歲少年玩3P。 <br />\n事發不久後，學校開始盛傳阿耶的淫蕩事蹟，檢警也介入調查。檢調分別調查8名涉及此案的少年少女，並發現與阿耶做愛的少年共有5人，目前阿耶已被逮捕。警方也說，本周三在逮捕阿耶的時候，發現阿耶喝得酩酊大醉。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170126/1043910/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170126%2F1043910%2F&d=LTuk7bByEYVromtWsWAKrGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=bb9adfea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170126/1043910/</a><br />\n慎入"},{"pid":"3c0d43912f11d2f64aba811d0062c90068174934","tid":96253,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b595496bca64b9ba7105fcad418a7d478877bde0","tid":96253,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:18:20.000Z","msg":"快啲強姦......"},{"pid":"d71aa259350b3c183741125e0eb47ff73e4f4fa9","tid":96253,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T22:57:43.000Z","msg":"40歲<br />\n冇相唔搶住"},{"pid":"7213fdddc960a433e91cf9632b6f73fab724b163","tid":96253,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T23:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快啲強姦......</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/27/070450_5b545c0168